messages.content: Yes, we need an officer right now. There's a man shooting at this lady. We need a cop.
I don't know where we are. Oh my gosh, what street is this called?
Okay, I hear you. I understand. Are you okay?
Please, I need an ambulance and police. We have babies around here too. There's babies in the car. He won't give them to the mom.
Alright. What happened? Is she hurt? Was she shot?
Yes, she's hurt. She's bleeding everywhere. She can't stand. She's fainting.
Okay, we will send EMS out. You said the address is 2711 10th Street?
He's shooting. He killed the kids! He killed!
Yes, no. He killed the babies. He killed them!
The babies! Oh my God, the babies!
Okay, stay on the line with me, please.
